{"tid":2441153,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實龍門依加既水準真係好左好多","createTime":"2021-03-10T12:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T06:42:44.000Z","uid":131368,"like":142,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5640f5b5c66c72a6299874f4bb6392245c6c9165","tid":2441153,"uid":131368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"見到出面個post我都想幫龍門講句野<br />\n我呢個荃灣JJ<br />\n差唔多一星期都食佢幾次<br />\n呢期好中意個炒滑蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好滑好好食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JunqROR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJunqROR.png&h=49700206&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZKXHVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZKXHVB.png&h=68ca3b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n54蚊包熱飲一個人<br />\n大大碟又足料<br />\n係路德圍黎講真係超值<br />\n隔離牛肉飯都差唔多價 但真係得牛肉飯<br />\n食炸雞就100一個人<br />\n食cafe pasta包杯檸蜜都80-100<br />\n台灣野食過一次好一般  奶茶唔好飲既 同好咸<br />\n除非你用3蚊豆花比架者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有次食常餐仲見到KA餐具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8S6BgH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8S6BgH.png&h=634cf013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但all day breakfast真係麻麻<br />\n大家真係唔洗試<br />\n食兩個常餐仲開心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JcgbNos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcgbNos.png&h=7d906257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日見到老闆<br />\n想同你講句<br />\n加油頂住呀<br />\n<br />\n成日想搵你影相但女朋友叫我唔好咁癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920781042a4269e32f5b2a12a85a47daa40407d4","tid":2441153,"uid":21545,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGMfuRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGMfuRt.jpg&h=d994358e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16394e27542b05d51918ebcfcb41c390bbbe7d14","tid":2441153,"uid":73381,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"920781042a4269e32f5b2a12a85a47daa40407d4","tid":2441153,"uid":21545,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGMfuRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGMfuRt.jpg&h=d994358e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBo5m6Fa.jpg&amp;h=1f043a13&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\npush"},{"pid":"f85d9f144f52a0b06352a552af112204cf60348c","tid":2441153,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae23c715d907c81e04ba1d725253716e2984e7fe","tid":2441153,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:30:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b85d79eacab9c93ba9dd2d24f126449a586a8e85","tid":2441153,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68296068d31348d907fbed6d91190dad1b486126","tid":2441153,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52858fc21253f0fb79ea01a4bbcfa2c91a23552","tid":2441153,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"頂丫咁靚既"},{"pid":"743cb81558da5e429f0c2e0ef9d2959f54b3b8f8","tid":2441153,"uid":31841,"like":4,"dislike":18,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"e52858fc21253f0fb79ea01a4bbcfa2c91a23552","tid":24