IZE}\" /><br />\n但all day breakfast真係麻麻<br />\n大家真係唔洗試<br />\n食兩個常餐仲開心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JcgbNos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcgbNos.png&h=7d906257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日見到老闆<br />\n想同你講句<br />\n加油頂住呀<br />\n<br />\n成日想搵你影相但女朋友叫我唔好咁癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"真係好多蛋 好抵食"},{"pid":"2d1979a7892b9eb339444ee84f9571130abe6929","tid":2441153,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b67b52e733ff713d2a2b0c662c5225e21df7feca","tid":2441153,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"佢係有心做既，運動高峰期嗰陣已經要有呢啲水準，而家太遲啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:43:06.000Z","msg":"閪杰cap尾水移民，完"},{"pid":"70d8b31ef6815599282c64381b16da0203dd74a3","tid":2441153,"uid":207080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa06aca9e66e27be9c46e6862d218a5a3a008f83","tid":2441153,"uid":38757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4910f4553fe1926970f22f059ce39a7c14c8b534","tid":2441153,"uid":51583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"626498f4a07689e7957616d4e6851b1567d1b9d3","tid":2441153,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老味,你句&quot;頂丫咁靚既&quot;假撚到<br />\n仲屎戲過D茄呢啡呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:07:18.000Z","msg":"浮誇有浮誇既效果<br />\n起碼多左你RE先啦<br />\n幫手推下POST係好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"其實我未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真係要試下先知<br />\n有人講難食 有人話ok<br />\n點都係自己試過先知<br />\n今個星期去試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"保證好食<br />\n除非你真係就咁我啲鹽泥食（好似arho tv 條on9 sunny 咁）"},{"pid":"320fe6e2216b7fe2432c5e5ee99a099c332f7b0b","tid":2441153,